uwsgi (2.0.11.2-3) experimental; urgency=medium

  * Update Vcs-* hints: Packaging moved to pkg-uwsgi Alioth group.
    Thanks to Riccardo Magliocchetti.
  * Fix build with Ruby 2.2:
    + Add new binary package uwsgi-plugin-rack-ruby2.2.
    + Temporarily tighten build-dependency on ruby-all-dev and ruby to
      versions where ruby2.2 is default, to succeed on sid+experimental
      build environments.
    + Fix old (pre-bug#755779 clarification) assumption that topmost
      listed Ruby kind is the default.
    Closes: Bug#791847. Thanks (again) to Christian Hofstaedtler.
  * Update supported archs:
    + Add ppc64el for mono.
  * Add patch cherry-picked upstream to fix apache 2.4 integration with
    unix domain sockets.
    Closes: bug#752783. Thanks to Alexandre Rossi.

